{"tid":259213,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"DC英雄片既奧斯卡級造型 已經甩開左Marvel個班幾條街","createTime":"2017-05-26T16:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T12:30:35.000Z","uid":119223,"like":23,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09b1b5268420d5a8429d37dfd2c9a5c6fe7e034b","tid":259213,"uid":119223,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"話說前排路過街口，離遠見到一位拾荒者推住車仔典下典下咁行緊過黎<br />\n<br />\n出於好奇，我決定走上前向呢位老漢送上慰問尋覓當中奇事<br />\n幾聲噓寒問暖下，發現老漢只不過剛好身染暑疾<br />\n<br />\n面臨結果如此普通之事，我亦只好交出500大元港紙加一句take care yourself便離去<br />\n<br />\n怎料老漢突吼一聲 : 恩人！請留步！<br />\n<br />\n我停下腳步轉身回望，只見老漢從車仔中找出一 Blu-ray 影碟交到我手上<br />\n<br />\n眼看包裝封面(Suicide Squad)<br />\n我低頭道 : 有何用意？<br />\n<br />\n老漢典下典下道 : 恩人！這正是你朝思暮想的奇事！<br />\n<br />\n我氣紅了臉 : 下~！<br />\n<br />\n老漢急道 : 恩人！前天鄙人路經此地，巧遇一少年拿着此影碟大吼大叫「仆你個街DLC！仆你個街DLC！」並憤然投倒在地，當我追上前交還時，少年只留下一句「狗都唔撚屌！」便曬着淚。奔了~<br />\n<br />\n我慨嘆道 : 奔了？如此影碟居然有令人發瘋的殺傷力？！可真奇事！奇事啊！<br />\n<br />\n我以上承輕功飛烏三叉步迅速趕回家，打開影碟<br />\n<br />\n幾個時辰後，好服裝好髮型好造型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腦海不斷來回發放同樣字句<br />\n戲中小隊等人完全是模特兒一般的存在<br />\n潮流界的尖端<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a3/Suicide_Squad_in_the_2016_film.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fa%2Fa3%2FSuicide_Squad_in_the_2016_film.jpg&h=7537d227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.joblo.com/posters/images/full/Suicide-Squad-character-poster-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joblo.com%2Fposters%2Fimages%2Ffull%2FSuicide-Squad-character-poster-10.jpg&h=9b3836eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女主角小丑女 劇組以高超技術為她化白面部<br />\n更以高超技巧染髮製作雙馬尾造型<br />\n配置一身淫蕩衣着<br />\n<br />\n男主角死射 劇組以精緻手法刪光男演員頭髮<br />\n更配上一個二媽巾面具<br />\n<br />\n二打六小丑 一身無腦kpop造型配上其沉穩地瘋癲的內在，帶出了一種社會與反社會之間的嘲諷與訴訟<br />\n<br />\n其餘成員更是單從外型已經看到角色深遠的背景，豐富的性格<br />\nGoogle之下，更發現此電影已經奪下奧斯卡化妝造型獎像<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blogs-images.forbes.com/scottmendelson/files/2017/03/Justice-League-DC-Films-Team-PosterB.jpg?width=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs-images.forbes.com%2Fscottmendelson%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F03%2FJustice-League-DC-Films-Team-PosterB.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960&h=9c67002a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CaBbFhlQ_EI/VV1OtgG5YVI/AAAAAAAABZQ/3o7OMEcKX-I/s1600/Bola%2BWorld%2B-%2BAgeofUltron.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CaBbFhlQ_EI%2FVV1OtgG5YVI%2FAAAAAAAABZQ%2F3o7OMEcKX-I%2Fs1600%2FBola%252BWorld%252B-%252BAgeofUltron.JPG&h=59c88391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我驚訝下搜尋DC英雄方的造型<br />\n看到後，我服了<br />\n他們完全脫離了我小時候的固有印象<br />\n一看之下，已經感受到他們帶來的活力和衝勁<br />\n<br />\n即使Marvel英雄並肩而站，面對DC英雄也只是外型如小丑般的存在<br />\n<br />\n奔了，奔了。"},{"pid":"5101cddfc32beb9bf07974c2f3951a4ed49390cc","tid":259213,"uid":11185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"深度既野你識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0636f74636eb8fc928fb58f48dc4668d941a90","tid":259213,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深度既野你識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好有外在"},{"pid":"490808d8665b7aca2c00cf58848d6fcab99b09bb","tid":259213,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"m記真係得iron man同spiderman 好少少，其他角色慘不忍睹"},{"pid":"6c4af4a981b605295790cd3bcb2477fe7c3a5f07","tid":259213,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe954491b0ee9f426af648296824a9d9e08629a2","tid":259213,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m記真係得iron man同spiderman 好少少，其他角色慘不忍睹</blockquote><br />\n<br /